âš ï¸ Important Notes
Warning: iptables commands can disrupt network connectivity if misconfigured. Always test in controlled environments and have backup access methods.

bash
# Safe practice: backup current rules before modifications
sudo iptables-save > iptables-backup.rules

# Restore if needed
sudo iptables-restore < iptables-backup.rules
